ZH: 中庸是儒家经典之一，是孔子的思想体系的核心之一。
EN: The Doctrine of the Mean is one of the classics of Confucianism and a core element of Confucius' philosophical system.

ZH: 中庸强调的是人要追求平衡、中立的处事态度。
EN: The Doctrine of the Mean emphasizes the pursuit of a balanced and neutral attitude in dealing with matters.

ZH: 在中庸的指导下，人们应该避免极端的行为和情绪。
EN: Under the guidance of the Doctrine of the Mean, people should avoid extreme behaviors and emotions.

ZH: 中庸主张的是以诚信为基础的人际关系。
EN: The Doctrine of the Mean advocates for interpersonal relationships based on sincerity and trustworthiness.

ZH: 在中庸的理念下，人们应该追求内外的和谐。
EN: In accordance with the principles of the Doctrine of the Mean, people should strive for harmony both internally and externally.

ZH: 中庸教导我们要有修身、齐家、治国、平天下的理念。
EN: The Doctrine of the Mean teaches us the principles of self-improvement, harmonious family life, good governance, and peace in the world.

ZH: 学习中庸有助于培养一个稳定、成熟的人格。
EN: Learning the Doctrine of the Mean helps cultivate a stable and mature personality.

