EN: In the concept of the Doctrine of the Mean, moral cultivation is an important subject in life.

ZH: 中庸讲求的是行为和情感的适度与适时。
EN: The Doctrine of the Mean emphasizes the moderation and timing of behavior and emotions.

ZH: 中庸强调的是人与人之间的和睦与尊重。
EN: The Doctrine of the Mean emphasizes harmony and respect among individuals.

